articles.author: Barry Schwartz
articles.title: Google previews WebMCP, a new protocol for AI agent interactions - Search Engine Land
articles.description: Google's WebMCP protocol lets AI agents execute structured actions on websites via browser APIs. Is this the next frontier of technical SEO?
articles.content:
Google today announced an early preview of WebMCP, a new protocol that defines how AI agents interact with websites.
